      "Classify: Distilled water, Milk, Iron nail.",
      "Why is '100' ambiguous regarding sig figs?"
    ],
    "didYouKnow": [
      "The term 'significant figure' was introduced to help scientists communicate the reliability of their data without writing long explanations every time."
    ],
    "summary": [
      "Matter is classified into pure substances and mixtures. Measurements must be reported with significant figures to reflect instrument precision."
    ],
    "quickRevision": [
